{"TopicDetails": {"type": 0, "ccm2Id": 46904272, "cftId": 0, "identifier": "CERV-2024-CHAR-LITI-WHISTLE", "title": "Supporting an enabling environment for the protection of whistleblowers", "publicationDateLong": 1710892800000, "callIdentifier": "CERV-2024-CHAR-LITI", "callTitle": "Promote civil society organisations\u2019 awareness of, capacity building and implementation of the EU Charter of Fundamental Rights", "callccm2Id": 46904303, "allowPartnerSearch": true, "frameworkProgramme": {"id": 43251589, "abbreviation": "CERV", "description": "Citizens, Equality, Rights and Values Programme (CERV)"}, "programmeDivision": [{"id": 44187987, "abbreviation": "CHAR-LITI", "description": "Promote capacity building and awareness on the EU Charter of Fundamental Rights"}], "topicMGAs": [], "tags": ["whistleblower reporting", "Directive on whistleblower protection", "legal remedies", "Directive (EU) 2019/1937"], "sme": false, "actions": [{"status": {"id": 31094502, "abbreviation": "Open", "description": "Open"}, "types": [{"typeOfAction": "CERV-PJG CERV Project Grants", "typeOfMGA": [{"id": 43249814, "abbreviation": "CERV-AG", "description": "CERV Action Grant Budget-Based"}]}], "plannedOpeningDate": "23 April 2024", "submissionProcedure": {"id": 31094504, "abbreviation": "single-stage", "description": "single-stage"}, "deadlineDates": ["18 September 2024"]}], "latestInfos": [{"approvalDate": "Apr 17, 2024 4:31:01 PM", "lastChangeDate": "Apr 17, 2024 4:31:01 PM", "content": "<p><strong><u><span lang=\"EN-GB\">CALL DOCUMENT TRANSLATIONS</span></u></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\">The French and German translations of the CERV-2024-CHAR-LITI Call document are available on the <a href=\"https://www.eacea.ec.europa.eu/document/607e4714-7e79-43fb-89c1-16270b5ce007_en\" target=\"_blank\">EACEA webpage</a>.<o:p></o:p></span></p>"}], "budgetOverviewJSONItem": {"budgetTopicActionMap": {"3542145": [{"action": "CERV-2024-CHAR-LITI-SPEECH - CERV-PJG CERV Project Grants", "plannedOpeningDate": "23 April 2024", "deadlineModel": "single-stage", "deadlineDates": ["18 September 2024"], "budgetYearMap": {"2024": 16000000}, "budgetTopicActionMap": {}}, {"action": "CERV-2024-CHAR-LITI-CHARTER - CERV-PJG CERV Project Grants", "plannedOpeningDate": "23 April 2024", "deadlineModel": "single-stage", "deadlineDates": ["18 September 2024"], "budgetYearMap": {"2024": 16000000}, "budgetTopicActionMap": {}}, {"action": "CERV-2024-CHAR-LITI-LITIGATION - CERV-PJG CERV Project Grants", "plannedOpeningDate": "23 April 2024", "deadlineModel": "single-stage", "deadlineDates": ["18 September 2024"], "budgetYearMap": {"2024": 16000000}, "budgetTopicActionMap": {}}, {"action": "CERV-2024-CHAR-LITI-CIVIC - CERV-PJG CERV Project Grants", "plannedOpeningDate": "23 April 2024", "deadlineModel": "single-stage", "deadlineDates": ["18 September 2024"], "budgetYearMap": {"2024": 16000000}, "budgetTopicActionMap": {}}, {"action": "CERV-2024-CHAR-LITI-WHISTLE - CERV-PJG CERV Project Grants", "plannedOpeningDate": "23 April 2024", "deadlineModel": "single-stage", "deadlineDates": ["18 September 2024"], "budgetYearMap": {"2024": 16000000}, "budgetTopicActionMap": {}}]}, "budgetYearsColumns": ["2024"]}, "description": "<SPAN class=\"topicdescriptionkind\">Scope</SPAN>:<p><strong>Supporting an enabling environment for the protection of whistleblowers</strong></p><p>A Union of values and rights is also based on effective law enforcement systems and the effective detection, investigation and prosecution of breaches of Union law. Support will be given to creating an enabling environment for reporting and informing on breaches of the Union law, in particular by building capacity on the effective application of the <strong>Directive on whistleblower protection</strong> (Directive (EU) 2019/1937). This Directive provides for an obligation to establish internal and external reporting channels, a strict obligation to maintain the confidentiality of the reporting person as well as for high standards of protection from retaliation and legal remedies for whistleblowers who report on breaches of EU law in a wide range of key policy areas, thus promoting the fundamental values of the rule of law and democracy as well as the right to freedom of expression, enshrined in Article 11 of the Charter.</p><p>Civil society organisations play a crucial role in help ensuring an effective implementation of these legal standards. Projects under this priority should support and protect whistleblowers and build capacity of national authorities and legal practitioners to ensure adequate legal remedies to protect whistleblowers.</p>\n", "conditions": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 153);\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">1.&nbsp;&nbsp; Eligible countries</span></b><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">:</span></span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;&#10;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#1F497D;mso-themecolor:text2;&#10;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\">&nbsp;as described in the <a href=\"https://ec.europa.eu/info/funding-tenders/opportunities/docs/2021-2027/cerv/wp-call/2024/call-fiche_cerv-2024-char-liti_en.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">Call document</a>.</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&#10;&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 153);\"><b style=\"text-indent: -18pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">2.&nbsp;&nbsp; Eligibility and admissibility conditions:</span></b></span><span style=\"text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(31, 73, 125);\"> as describe</span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; text-indent: -18pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(31, 73, 125);\">d in the <a href=\"https://ec.europa.eu/info/funding-tenders/opportunities/docs/2021-2027/cerv/wp-call/2024/call-fiche_cerv-2024-char-liti_en.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">Call document</a>.</span>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 153);\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold; font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">3.&nbsp; &nbsp;Proposal page limits and layout:</span></span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;&#10;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#1F497D;mso-themecolor:text2;&#10;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\">&nbsp;Please refer to Part B of the standard proposal template.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 153);\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">4.&nbsp; &nbsp;Evaluation:</span></b></span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&#10;&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#1F497D;mso-themecolor:text2;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\">&nbsp;Evaluation criteria, scoring, threshold and&nbsp;process are described in the <a href=\"https://ec.europa.eu/info/funding-tenders/opportunities/docs/2021-2027/cerv/wp-call/2024/call-fiche_cerv-2024-char-liti_en.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">Call document</a>.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:18.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;line-height:&#10;normal\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 153);\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">5.&nbsp;&nbsp; Indicative timetable for evaluation and grant agreement:</span></b></span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;&#10;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#1F497D;mso-themecolor:text2;&#10;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\"> as described in the <a href=\"https://ec.europa.eu/info/funding-tenders/opportunities/docs/2021-2027/cerv/wp-call/2024/call-fiche_cerv-2024-char-liti_en.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">Call document</a>.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" s